high_descs: Turn to the right, move forward toward the door, then turn to the right and face the coffee table.
Pick up the newspaper to the right of the toy dog from the coffee table.
Turn left and move towards the door then turn right and move towards the couch, then turn left towards the wall, and then turn right and move towards the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a newspaper by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Turn right, take a step forward, turn right and walk forward, then turn right to face the brown coffee table.
Pick up the newspaper on the coffee table.
Turn left and walk to the dark brown shelves, turn right, walk forward to the tall lamp in the left corner of the room.
Turn on the lamp and examine the newspaper.
anns.task_desc: Examine the newspaper by the light of the tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the coffee table in the middle of the room
Pick up the newspaper from the coffee table
Continue to walk around the coffee table to the floor lamp in the corner of the room
anns.task_desc: Examine the newspaper under the light of the floor lamp
